title: Noam Chomsky vs Alan Dershowitz debate - Where do we go from her
description:
Hey all,

If I could recommend one Chomsky file, this would be it.
I know it's been uploaded before but the previous torrents are dead now.

Here is a summary of the debate:
http://www.news.harvard.edu/gazette/2005/12.01/31-chomsky.html

For opening the file, I recommend KMPlayer, which can be downloaded here:
http://kmplayer.en.softonic.com/


I haven't seen Dershowitz this humiliated since Norman Finkelstein debated him on Democracy now!. Except this time, the debate is held in Harvard, where Dershowitz is a professor of law.



Enjoy and seed,


// luft
